description: Welcome to Tag Team Tuesday. This week Lisa Tiffian and Yasmine Loven take ok Daisy Ducati and Andre Shakti. With all this Tit and Ass on Team Tarrasque, the Grapplers are in for some smoothering. This match only goes 2 rounds. One wrestler take a heavy hit and since the team captain for the Tarrasques didn't attend, it's an unfair advantage to put a fresh Darling in to replace her injured player
title: Team Tarrasque vs Team Grappler eps. 3
